# MSAccess VCS Add-in Project

This repository contains the MSAccess Version Control System (VCS) Add-in for Microsoft Access.

For comprehensive guidance on working with this codebase, read these files:

@AGENTS.md - Main project guide covering architecture, coding standards, and development workflow
@Version Control.accda.src/AGENTS.md - Guide for working with exported Access database source files

## Quick Reference

- All VBA source files use **UTF-8 with BOM** encoding - this is critical for import
- New component types implement the `IDbComponent` interface
- Use the `T()` function for all user-facing strings (translation support)
- Error handling: use `DebugMode(True)`, `LogUnhandledErrors`, and `CatchAny` patterns
- Naming: `mod*` for modules, `cls*` for classes, `frm*` for forms, `I*` for interfaces
